OL,4,CChristmas party settles case for
OL,5,C#36,000
OL,7,FA woman who "experienced unwanted and
OL,8,Finappropriate physical contact" from a
OL,9,Fcolleague at a work Christmas event
OL,10,Fhas been awarded #36,000.
OL,12,FFernanda Hermosilla settled her case
OL,13,Fagainst a colleague for #21,000 and
OL,14,Fagainst her employer, the Northern
OL,15,FIreland Human Rights Commission, for
OL,16,F#15,000.
OL,18,FMs Hermosilla, who was supported by
OL,19,Fthe Equality Commission for Northern
OL,20,FIreland, attended a staff Christmas
OL,21,Fdinner in December 2022.
