OL,4,CChristmas party settles case for
OL,5,C#36,000
OL,7,FShe said, during the evening, she
OL,8,Fexperienced unwanted and inappropriate
OL,9,Fphysical contact from a colleague,
OL,10,Fwhich was witnessed by other
OL,11,Fcolleagues.
OL,13,FWhen she returned to work on Monday
OL,14,Fmorning, she was informed by her
OL,15,Femployer that an investigation into
OL,16,Fevents during that evening was being
OL,17,Fconducted after the colleague who had
OL,18,Fwitnessed the incident made a formal
OL,19,Fcomplaint.
