OL,5,C#36,000
OL,7,FDuring the investigation, Ms
OL,8,FHermosilla said she advised her
OL,9,Femployer of an earlier incident of
OL,10,Finappropriate touching, at a non-work
OL,11,Fevent, that she said happened a few
OL,12,Fweeks before with the same colleague
OL,13,Fat a Belfast nightclub.
OL,15,FMs Hermosilla said she had been very
OL,16,Fupset following that incident but had
OL,17,Fbeen reluctant to make a complaint
OL,18,Fbecause she was new to her role.
