OL,7,FMs Hermosilla also advised her
OL,8,Femployer of comments made to her by
OL,9,Fthe same colleague of a racial and
OL,10,Fpolitical nature, which she also found
OL,11,Fto be inappropriate. This was also
OL,12,Finvestigated by her employer.
OL,14,FThe cases were settled without
OL,15,Fadmission of liability.
OL,17,FMs Hermosilla described "a very
OL,18,Fdifficult time" but said she was glad
OL,19,Fshe "took a stand".
