OL,7,F"I did not want or ask for any of
OL,8,Fthis. I was excited to move to Belfast
OL,9,Fto start a new job and advance my
OL,10,Fcareer. This has been a very stressful
OL,11,Fexperience," she said.
OL,13,F"But I'm glad that I took a stand.
OL,14,FEveryone must know what unacceptable
OL,15,Fbehaviour is and what I experienced
OL,16,Fwas wrong.
