OL,7,F"I want other women to know that they
OL,8,Fdon't have to accept this type of
OL,9,Fbehaviour in the office or at work
OL,10,Fparties and that they should always
OL,11,Fexpect to be supported appropriately
OL,12,Fby their employer.
OL,14,F"I'm glad my case is resolved and now
OL,15,FI want to put this behind me and move
OL,16,Fon with my life."
