OL,7,FGeraldine McGahey, chief commissioner,
OL,8,FEquality Commission for Northern
OL,9,FIreland, said employers must ensure
OL,10,Fthe safety and dignity of staff at
OL,11,FChristmas parties.
OL,13,F"We are currently in the middle of the
OL,14,FChristmas party season. We know that
OL,15,Fstaff parties and outings are
OL,16,Fimportant for team building and for
OL,17,Frecognition and reward, but employers
OL,18,Fmust ensure that everyone attending is
OL,19,Fsafe and that their dignity is
OL,20,Frespected," she said.
